# CLAUDE.md — Product Context Template

> Copy this file to your project root as `CLAUDE.md` and fill in your product details.
> Every skill and agent reads this file automatically to understand your product context.

## Shipwright Auto-Start

When a new Claude Code session begins, run `/start` to launch the Shipwright orchestrator.
The orchestrator greets the PM, asks what they're working on, builds an execution plan
using the skills map, and dispatches agents on approval.

To enable this behavior, add the following to your `.claude/settings.json`:

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "session_start": [
      { "command": "/start" }
    ]
  }
}
```

Or simply type `/start` at the beginning of each session.

